      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "concerning",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Him, but the genitive (which is here found in the original) implies also that they had claimed to be God’s special ministers and witnesses.",
